data.description: I must emphasize on the most GORGEOUS views from your backyard!! Idaho living at its best in the most quaint, quiet popular town of Fairfield. You are in the center of it all! Camping , fishing, hunting, skiing, snowmobiling, with Sun Valley near. A short commute to Bellevue of only 36 minutes and 17 minutes to your nearest ski area. Sunsets will be enjoyed on the covered back patio while you have the views of Soldier Mountain and the open field in your backyard. What better way to be comforted in the winter months than snuggled next to your wood stove while watching the snow fall. This home offers an open concept of 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, 2 car garage. LVP flooring throughout the home, tile flooring in the kitchen. Call your favorite realtor today to view this home!
